data.description: A beautifully renovated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home sits in a quiet & charming neighborhood southwest of Carbondale. The unique architecture gives instant curb appeal. You first walk into a stylish kitchen where you can see into the open concept living room area. Stainless steel appliances, a smart water heater, & a 70 inch smart TV are just a few perks that come with this home! There are spacious bedrooms as you walk up the stairs, and plenty of room for storage. Did I mention the master suite has its very own balcony? Sit out on the private space to enjoy the view of the fenced in backyard and the serenity of the trees. The backyard features a fire pit, a smoker, & a pool! The seller is leaving  a lot of extra items like extra boxes of flooring and paint. There is a lot to see here in this delightful 2 story home! Call today for a showing!!
